<html>
<head>
  <meta charset='utf-8'>
  <style>
  p {
    font-family: Courier;
    color: rgb(200,100,0);
  }
  ul {
    font-family: Courier;
    color: rgb(30,80,122);
  }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <p>Hey <%= firstName %>,</p>
  <p>
    How are you doing? I'm doing well. It's been about <%= numMonthsSinceContact %> months
    since we last talked. This is an auto-generated email I learned how to make in the web development immersive class at Fullstack Academy.
  </p>
  <p>
    I've been blogging about my experiences at Fullstack on my Tumblr. 
    Check out my most recent posts:
    <ul>
      <% for(var i=0; i<latestPosts.length; i++) {%>
         <li><%= latestPosts[i].date %>: <a href=<%= latestPosts[i].post_url %>> <%= latestPosts[i].title %></a>  </li>
      <% } %>
    </ul>
  </p>
  <p>
    Talk soon,<br>
    Michal
  </p>
</body>
</html>